a.n: Agent Binky: Pets of the Universe I (17)

p.k: Chew Chew Challenge The team notices small aliens (code name: termites) eating Small Human’s new treehouse and get on a mission to evict them.
p.d: Binky is an indoor cat who is a member of a secret agency. Teamed with like-minded pet agents, they are on a mission to keep their humans and "space station" safe from "aliens".
